  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You carve glowing runes into your skin, which become dormant until activated. As an attack action, you can lower your Chakra and maximum Chakra Pool by up to 3, containing it within the seal. You cannot lower your Chakra below 1 this way. The seals help lower your Chakra Signature, and are not detected by creatures sensing Chakra. Each seal can hold no more than 3 Chakra.<br><br>As a move action, you can cancel any number of these seals currently holding Chakra to immediately restore your maximum Chakra Pool and current Chakra by the amount released. When a seal's duration expires, the Chakra is released in this manner as well. You take 2 damage every time you attempt to perform this technique.</p>\n\n\n\n",
